text: Pizy was a municipality in the Swiss canton of Vaud. It was in the district of Morges. Pizy became part of the municipality of Aubonne on 1 July 2011.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz published by the Swiss Federal Statistical Office accessed 17 February 2011 == References == Category:2011 disestablishments in Switzerland Category:Former municipalities of Vaud
title: Pizy
